  • Constructor Details

    • BreakerADIS16448

      public BreakerADIS16448()
      ADIS16448 gyro with Z axis as yaw, MXP SPI port, and calibration time of 512 ms.

    • BreakerADIS16448

      public BreakerADIS16448​(edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.ADIS16448_IMU.IMUAxis yawAxis, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.SPI.Port port, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.ADIS16448_IMU.CalibrationTime calTime)
      ADIS16448 with custom parameters. All axes are inverted to match the orientations shown in the linked image, regardless of which axis is defined as the yaw. https://wiki.analog.com/_media/first/adis16448_rotation_figure.jpg?w=400&tok=8704ca
      Parameters:
      yawAxis - Which axis will be the yaw.
      port - SPI port.
      calTime - Calibration time.
